                        "id": "18429137710115272",
                        "text": "Comment \u201cJAPAN\u201d for a Google Map link of the store!\n\nIf money is no object, this should be your first stop for gifts while you\u2019re in Tokyo. \n\nLocated in the heart of Harajuku, this is where you\u2019ll find some of the coolest handmade products that are normally too hard to find or just not easy to get anywhere else. \n\nThis company is famously known for producing and sourcing made in Japan products, which means you\u2019ll find incredible artisan pieces you won\u2019t see anywhere else. \n\nFrom @a.craft86 x @sashiko_gals daruma, hand crafted kendama, and @studiodartisan / @yamane.industries.shop denim, you\u2019ll find one of a kind pieces at this store. \n\u2014\nIG:\u00a0@japan_edition_official\nHARAJUKU: 12PM-8PM\nKYOTO: 11AM-8PM\n\n#tokyo\u00a0#craftsman #daruma #kendama #denim"
                    }
                }
            ]
